title: Raunak Farhaz
text:
Hello! Hallo! Hola! Ciao!
I am Raunak and I am currently doing my doctorate in Theoretical Chemistry in Humboldt-Universit√§t zu Berlin. I am a method developer, primarily focussing in the field of Multiresolution-Resolution Analysis. I love computers and programming and I have an expertise in Fortran77, C++, Julia and Python. Besides science I love to cook and am an avid music lover, I play guitar and uke.
I love teaching, hence you will find my tutorial videos and lecture notes in the teaching section of this website.
For relevant research collaboration please contact me through my email.
Nice to meet you !
